title: 666. Daniel Jeremiah's Mock Draft 3.0
itunes:title: 666. Daniel Jeremiah's Mock Draft 3.0
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this special show, Daniel Jeremiah gives a breakdown of his full first round 2021 NFL Mock Draft 3.0. Find out which quarterbacks will go in the first round, which position group is the deepest and how far surprise players, such as Mac Jones, are moving up the draft board. Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
